text: Hansjörg Aemisegger (born 18 February 1952) is a Swiss former racing cyclist. He was the Swiss National Road Race champion in 1979. He also rode in the men's road race at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male cyclists Category:People from Winterthur Category:Olympic cyclists of Switzerland Category:Cyclists at the 1976 Summer Olympics
